OL,3,CMan shoots boyfriend in the head after
OL,4,Crow over cigarettes and sandwiches
OL,6,FA man has been jailed after shooting
OL,7,Fhis boyfriend in the head with an air
OL,8,Fgun after a row over cigarettes and
OL,9,Fsandwiches.
OL,11,FKen Richardson held the weapon up to
OL,12,FMartin Sharp's head and shot him -
OL,13,Fafter Mr Sharp had ignored
OL,14,FRichardson's offer to make him a
OL,15,Fsandwich, three times.
OL,17,FThe couple had rowed minutes earlier,
OL,18,Fafter Mr Sharp caught Richardson
OL,19,Ftaking his cigarettes.
