OL,6,FMr Sharp was rushed to James Cook
OL,7,FUniversity Hospital, in Middlesbrough
OL,8,Fon 27 March, but surgeons decided it
OL,9,Fwas safer to leave the pellet lodged
OL,10,Fin his skull.
OL,12,FRichardson, 44, appeared at Teesside
OL,13,FCrown Court, via video link from
OL,14,FDurham prison, on Thursday morning (19
OL,15,FSeptember).
OL,17,FHe was originally facing an attempted
OL,18,Fmurder charge, but the court accepted
OL,19,Fhis guilty pleas to causing grievous
OL,20,Fbodily harm with intent and to the
OL,21,Fpossession of a firearm with intent.
