OL,3,CMan shoots boyfriend in the head after
OL,4,Crow over cigarettes and sandwiches
OL,6,FThe court heard that the couple have
OL,7,Fbeen in an on-off relationship for
OL,8,Fmany years, and that Richardson was
OL,9,Fstruggling with poor mental health and
OL,10,Fdrug addiction.
OL,12,FMr Sharp let Richardson move in to
OL,13,Fhelp him - but Richardson ended up
OL,14,Fbecoming Mr Sharp's carer after the
OL,15,Fvictim developed a bad back.
