OL,3,CMan shoots boyfriend in the head after
OL,4,Crow over cigarettes and sandwiches
OL,6,FRichardson had asked his partner for
OL,7,Fsome cigarettes and Mr Sharp had given
OL,8,Fhim some on the evening of 26 March-
OL,9,F but he said that when he woke up the
OL,10,Fnext morning, he caught Richardson
OL,11,Ftaking more.
OL,13,FMr Sharp said that he picked up the
OL,14,Fcigarette packet and "threw it behind
OL,15,Fhim." He later ignored Richardson's
OL,16,Foffer of a sandwich.
OL,18,FIn a statement read out to the court,
OL,19,FMr Sharp said: "The next thing I heard
OL,20,Fa loud sound to my head.
