OL,6,F"I turned and looked and I saw the
OL,7,Fbarrel of my air rifle inches from my
OL,8,Fface."
OL,10,FMr Sharp rang the police at 6.45am;
OL,11,Fand Richardson was found waiting
OL,12,Foutside "with his bags packed" when
OL,13,Fofficers arrived at the Hartlepool
OL,14,Fhome.
OL,16,FIn a letter, the victim asked the
OL,17,Fjudge to hand Richardson a lenient
OL,18,Fsentence. "I believe it was his mental
OL,19,Fhealth that caused him to do what he
OL,20,Fdid" Mr Sharp said.
