OL,6,FA psychiatrist's report found that
OL,7,FRichardson may have been suffering
OL,8,Ffrom psychosis at the time. Richardson
OL,9,Fhimself said he was "hearing voices
OL,10,Fbecause of all of the drugs" he had
OL,11,Ftaken.
OL,13,FJudge Timothy Stead told Richardson
OL,14,Fthat his victim "has done something
OL,15,Fwhich is unusual. He feels a degree of
OL,16,Fblame for the situation himself and
OL,17,Fthere were clearly domestic strains at
OL,18,Fthe time.
